It is an application which simplifies the task of creating a personal resume. The system is flexible to use, and reduces the need to think and design a suitable resume based on qualifications. The program is designed to provide a simple means of creating a resume that looks professional. Individuals just need to fill details on consoleÂ that sets out questions from all the required fields such as personal questions, educational, values, interest, abilities, etc. The answers provided by the users are stored and a well-structured resume is automatically generated on the desktop in PDF format.

There are 3 main packages:
1. DAO - Data Access Object package which provides the defination of all classes and its attribute
2. BO - Business Object which describes all the functionalities and logic of the system
3. MAIN - This main package provides the entry point to the system execution.
